# DualFrontier analyzer shipped severities — Release 1.0 (A'.9.1 Phase γ; F-12
# ratified 2026-07-01). Explicit restatement of the 17 descriptor defaultSeverity
# values (descriptor-as-truth; no override semantics — a key differing from its
# descriptor is a defect). Registry: ANALYZER_RULES §4.1 (rule registry); release
# record: tools/DualFrontier.Analyzers/AnalyzerReleases.Shipped.md.
# `suggestion` here == DiagnosticSeverity.Info (DFL025_B — IDE-only).
